                    this.addLog("SDKå¯åŠ¨å¤±è´¥");
                    this.addLog("errMessage:" + ret.errMessage);
                }
            });
        },
        stopSDK() {
            this.addLog("å…³é—­SDK");
            netshieldNativePlugin.stopNetshieldService();
            this.addLog("SDKå·²å…³é—­");
        },
        browse() {
            const localhostPort = netshieldNativePlugin.getLocalhostPort("240.0.0.2;80");
            let url = "http://127.0.0.1:" + localhostPort;
            this.addLog("è®¿é—®é¡µé¢: " + url);
            uni.request({

                    this.addLog('è¯·æ±‚æˆåŠŸ:' + res.data);
                },
                fail: (err) => {

                }
            })
        }
    }
